{
  "stem": "1581.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And these rumors, which is a [NON-ENGLISH], flew around and made our mood bearable because long before the real McCoy happened, Sicily was invaded, and Italy was invaded, and they landed in the south of France, and-- and God knows what optimistic fairy tales, and Berlin was bombed and Dresden was bombed, and this was all holidays for us when the Germans were hit.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All these [NON-ENGLISH] brought news of things that were bound to happen sooner or later.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Only in our dreams and wishes, they happened much earlier.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were deported after the embellishment of Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I want to dwell a little on the embellishment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Theresienstadt was a miserable place to be.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were full of old and sick people, and there was ridiculously low rations of food, and theoretically you could not survive on the ration.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That my mother stayed alive was only because I supplied her with additional food because I had, through my profession, access to additional food.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My wife survived her tuberculosis because I could feed her properly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the rest of the population was in very miserable misery.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was dysentery.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was hunger.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was cold.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was depression and exhaustion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And people died like flies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They died in their sleep, and they died standing in line for food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They died working.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we had an enormous mortality rate every day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Theresienstadt was-- as overcrowded as it was, mother nature took care of it by an enormous mortality rate and the transport emptied it out, but new transport kept on coming in.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So finally in 1944, it somehow settled down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All of a sudden there were no transports and once there were no transport, we-- our mothers were gone.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were just the three of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
